text: Albert Victor Walsh (31 January 1877 – 21 June 1956) was an Australian rules footballer who played for the Collingwood Football Club in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * *Albert Walsh's profile at Collingwood Forever Category:1877 births Category:1956 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Collingwood Football Club players
